{
  "stem": "1704.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 250.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at the end it wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He only had little attacks and had it under control.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've got Herman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He'll be here later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's the oldest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sarah, that's my daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She might be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I had David and Lester and Louis, he'll be here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Louis, and Jacqueline.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Australia really itself hasn't done much, but being here-- I need them, let me put it that way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't need Australia to do things for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But being here and being free and having the children, it's a good country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me put it that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the last year I start to feel my age a little bit, but it's not nothing serious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, because I'm 75.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, little, little, little complaints, not serious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I've had one operation on the, on the buttock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a cyst there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the doctors reckon it was a dirty needle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, well, that's possible, because when I had the typhoid, I had plenty of needles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, I had the operation '50, in about '55, 1956.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a cyst on the buttock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What struck me was the old cars you saw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had beautiful clothes with me for the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't see any nice clothes here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very far behind, I reckon, with everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, I remember on, near Museum Station, you know, they had the police in a high, like in a-- like a house on stilts, that regulating the traffic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no traffic lights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the first thing we noticed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we've come a long way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I'll tell you, they still don't think much of Australia overseas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had a letter from a cousin the other day, and she said-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
